        {
            "title": "交易員押注聯儲會降息步伐將加快 為經濟數據和主席人選的敲定布倉",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/f3imXq6w2lX1loX8sEnHgA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/733348261dafe51707823d8ab71812f0\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 交易員們正在集中押注，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>新主席的任命以及延遲的經濟數據在本月的發布將支持總統唐納德·川普的降息呼聲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在美國期貨市場，與擔保隔夜融資利率(SOFR)掛鉤的短期利率曲線結構的需求正在增加，其密切反映市場對聯儲會利率決策結果的預期。這些押注反映出，在主席傑羅姆·鮑威爾明年5月任期結束後，貨幣政策寬鬆步伐可能加快。明年6月17日的聲明將是新任聯儲會主席上任後的首次公開表態。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自白宮國家經濟委員會主任凱文·哈塞特成為接替鮑威爾的熱門人選後，市場開始佈局新倉位。川普周二在內閣會議上稱，聯儲會主席的角逐已「縮小到一人」，並稱哈塞特為「潛在的聯儲會主席」。他表示將在明年初宣布最終決定。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-615c9d74-b20b-3a61-a3ea-627b851ce71e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5rGaRiyth3X8yrJsmb0f9A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/f11ab7b9821aab012ed41b4f47de10ce\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Man Group首席市場策略師Kristina Hooper本周寫道，該聲明「將催生一位‘影子聯儲會主席’」，「這可能使聯儲會傳達貨幣政策的能力複雜化，並在市場亟需明確指引之際引起困惑」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在槓桿化期貨市場中，交易員們已經開始推演各種情景，周一一項SOFR期貨蝶式結構出現了一名巨量買家，是一年多以來該結構規模最大的交易。隨著交易員為進一步降息做準備，近期交易時段中，3個月、6個月和12個月SOFR利差相關的交易活動也頗為活躍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推動期貨利差波動的不僅是聯儲會新主席人選。高盛策略師正為12月16日將公佈的11月勞動力市場數據提前佈局對沖策略。該數據因美國政府停擺而延遲，如果證實近期放緩的跡象，可能引發更多鴿派押注。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trader Bets Swell on Trump-Backed Fed, Data Stoking US Rate Cuts</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Carter Johnson、Ye Xie.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%93%A1%E6%8A%BC%E6%B3%A8%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E6%AD%A5%E4%BC%90%E5%B0%87%E5%8A%A0%E5%BF%AB-%E7%82%BA%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%B8%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B2%E5%AE%9A%E5%B8%83%E5%80%89-110724715.html",
